      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N ta KUnga Wahrdß\nnotikke ohtrā Reisē uhs\nJonasu/ un fazztja:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zellees/ eij uhs Niniwt to\nteełu Pilsfahtu./ un fluddina\nprett winnu to Sluddinascha-\nnu/ fo es uhs tew runnaju."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahß Jonag/ un\ngahje uhs Niniwi pehz ta KUN-\nGA Wahrdu/ bet Niniwe bija\nweens leels Deewa Pilsfahtß no\ntrejo Deenu Gahjunteem."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jonas fahze Pilsfah-\ntā eet weenas Deenas Gahju-\nmu/ un fluddinaja/ un fazztja:\nWehl tschetrdesmits Deenas irr/\ntad taps Nintwe apgahsta."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tizzeja tee Laudis no\nNinives eeksch Deewa / un iṣ-\ntauze weenu Gaweschannu / un\naptehrpahß ar Maißeem/ tik lab-\nbi Leeli ka Masi."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tad tas Wahrdß\npreeksch ta Kehnixa no Ninives\nnahze/ tad zehlahß wiꞥſch no fa-\nwa Gohdn- Krehsfa / un nolikke\nfawas Kehnixa Drehbeß no fe-\nwin/ un apwike weenu Maisn/\nun apfehdahß Pelnds."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch likke isfaukt /\nun eekschNinives tappe fazzihts/\nzaur ta Kehnixa un winna Leel-\nKungu Pawehleschann/ un pee-\nfazzihts: Ne lai nedß Zilweks /\nnedß Lohps/ jeb Wehrfts / jeb\nAws ne masbanda/ lai tee Gan-\nnōs ne eet/ nedß Uhdeni dserx."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Zilweki un Lohpt laid\nar Maißeem apfedjahß/ un Dee-\nwu gauschi peefauz/ un lai tee\natgreeſchahß ikweens no fawa\nnikna Zelta/ un no ta Warras-\nDarba/ kas winnu Rokfāß ir-\nraid."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ko finn/ jaichu Deews at-\ngreeſfees / un winnam schehl\nnahſfees/ un nogreeſfees no ta\nKarstuma fawas Duſmibas / ka\nmehs bohjā ne eetam."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews redſeja winnu\nDarbus/ ka tee no fawa nikna\nZelta atgreeſahß/ un Deewam\nnahzahß schehl wiꞥſch tas Kan-\nnuns / ko wiꞥſch bija runnajs\nteem darriht/ un ne darrija to."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta IV. Modalla.\nJonas apſtaistahß/ ka ta Gohdiba pahr Niniwi\nne nahk: 1. Bet Deews parahda win-\nnam zour to Sihmi weena nokalnscha Aug-\nta ar kuplahm Lappahm: 6. Ka wiꞥſch\nbes Wainas dusmo: 10."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "As reebe Jonatam ar\ngauschas Reebschanas /\nJun winna Duſniba ap-\nkattahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pecuhdse to\nKUNGII / un fazztja : Ak\nKUNGS! woj es to ne fazziju/\ntad es wehl fawā Semmē biju/\ntapehz es papreekſchu steidsohs\nuhs Tarsu behgt/ jo es finnaju/\nka tu effi weens schehligs un\ntirdsschehligs Deews/ lehnprah-\ntigs un no leelas Schehlastibas/\nkaim tasLaunums schehl nahkahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nu tad KUNGS! jeimt\nmannu Dwehfeli no mannim /\nEee 2"
    }
  ],
